<br />
The fact that they &quot;nerfed&quot; cv over a 10% group dps boost for sorc was not a bad idea but was not enough to cover the dps/survivability/group utility that necros or druids can offer in groups or raids. <br />
<br />
I still believe as some of you have written as well that developers &quot;disregard&quot; communities and forums and form their own ideas about revamps that will kind of not go down well with our community. <br />
<br />
SOme change still do exist on the test server such as the new increased flame spear damage (36m range) and asaya's scorn but they will be removed totally in the next patch or when gu5 goes live.<br />
<br />
The least they can do is to leave these 2 changes now till gu6 comes cause every litttle bit of help will help to our suffering of waiting for another 6 weeks for the next gu.
                  
